    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Studio Workflow</p>
      <h1>Signal Chain</h1>
      <p class="content-intro__lede">Every instrument's path from its physical output to its Ableton Live track, including connection type, input assignment, and gain staging target.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="content-intro__actions">
      <a href="/gear/motu-ultralite-mk3" class="button-secondary">MOTU Overview</a>
    </div>
  </section>

